      "raw_text": "CHICAGO, June 9.-R. Insinger\nof Spokane, chairman of the board\nof governors of the National Irriga-\nton congress, addressing the Han\nnibal club, declared that in nine\nyears the reclamation act will have\nresulted in the reclamation of\n5000 900 acres of land and the\ncompletion of 10 reclamation prof\nects now held in allegiance."
